      "title": "Singapore President congratulates President Wickremesinghe",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The President of the Republic of Singapore Halimah Yacob congratulated President Ranil Wickremesinghe on his assumption of duties as the 08th Executive President of Sri Lanka.",
        "The Singapore President thanked President Ranil Wickremesinghe for his message sent on the 08th of August 2022 on the occasion of Singapore\u2019s 57th National Day, said the President's Media Division on Friday (2).",
        "President Halimah Yacob also wished President Ranil Wickremesinghe success in his new appointment.",
        "It\u2019s a good budget \u2013 Mahinda Rajapaksa on Budget Amendment 2022",
        "Chinese Fertilizer: Auditor General recommends to recover losses; prosecute those responsible"
